content:
Give Non-Agents Access to Messaging for In-App and Web Transcripts

To let non-agents view Messaging for In-App and Web transcripts, give them access to the Messaging Session record and give them the Access Conversation Entries app permission.

Available in: Lightning Experience. 
This article applies to: Messaging for In-App and Messaging for Web channels
Give your non-agent user access to the Messaging Session record.
From Setup, search for Profiles, and select Profiles.
Select the name of the profile for your non-agents.
Select App Permissions.
Click Edit.
Select Enable on the Access Conversation Entries permission.
Save your changes.
title: Granting Non-Agent Access to Messaging Transcripts
